  "title": "Contracts Manager (LNG)",
  "description": "<p>Newly created role with a leading energy trading firm. The role will have extensive exposure to LNG contracts review and interfacing the traders.<br /><br /><strong>Responsibilities</strong><br />As part of a wider team, you will be drafting and reviewing LNG contracts and take a proactive approach in managing the contracts management life cycle.<br /><br />There are existing templates in place, and this role would work commercially with various relevant departments to ensure transactions move smoothly.<br /><br /><strong>Requirements</strong><br />At least 4 years relevant experience in the LNG sector, and familiar with the relevant terms and clauses.<br />A dynamic enterprising individual who can handle the rigor and pace of a large MNC would would suit this role.<br /><br /><strong>To Apply</strong><br />Interest and referrals to co@kerryconsulting.com<br />Reg: R1544641 Lic: 16S8060</p>",
